description: Lists all the versions of a detector model. Only the metadata associated with each detector model version is returned.

parameters.name: detectorModelName
parameters.description: The name of the detector model whose versions are returned.

nested_items.name: detectorModelVersionSummaries
nested_items.description: Summary information about the detector model versions.

nested_items.name: detectorModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the detector model.

nested_items.name: detectorModelVersion
nested_items.description: The ID of the detector model version.

nested_items.name: detectorModelArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the detector model version.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the role that grants the detector model permission to perform its tasks.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time the detector model version was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The last time the detector model version was updated.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the detector model version.

nested_items.name: evaluationMethod
nested_items.description: Information about the order in which events are evaluated and how actions are executed.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token that you can use to return the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
